snippet.textDisplay: I'm absolutely impressed with this comeback. Sadly the last few songs of them didn't capture me but this comeback brought me back to the thought that they can be so genius with music. I absolutely love how artistic black swan is. The song is subtle but powerful and strong. And the choreography is amazing. On the other side we have ON, which is more energetic but as awesome as black Swan. They remind me of their old days but much stronger. I can proudly say that I admire their work and I'm super happy with this creation their present us.
